Recommended Sizes

Cubit: 100-300 lines
Repository: 100-400 lines
Page: 50-150 lines
View: 100-250 lines
Widget: 50-150 lines

When to Split
If a file exceeds these guidelines:

Extract helper methods to separate files
Split complex widgets into smaller ones
Create separate view files for different sections
Consider if the class has too many responsibilities


