 Create model/data/ for DTOs with JsonSerializable
 Create model/repositories/ with abstract and implementation
 Create view/ with page, views, and widgets folders
 Create barrel files (widgets.dart, views.dart) for exports
 Register dependencies in {feature}_di.dart
 Add feature DI setup call in core/di/service_locator.dart


ğŸ“ Key Principles

Feature-First: Organize by feature, not by layer
Single Responsibility: One concept per file
Consistent Naming: Always use snake_case for files
Flat Structure: Avoid deep nesting
Barrel Files: Clean exports for related files
Clear Separation: Each folder has a clear purpose

Follow these conventions strictly for consistency across the entire codebase.